rows.label: qev085609_MSG0001
rows.name: Seems the UM response was coming from this plant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0002
rows.name: The data collection's finished. I'll upload it to FrontierNav.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0003
rows.name: All right. Let's head to the next spot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0004
rows.name: Right![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0005
rows.name:
...Okay, we're done analyzing this one, too.
I'll put it up on FrontierNav.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0006
rows.name: Just one to go.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0007
rows.name: Let's knock it out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0008
rows.name: ...Right. Upload to FrontierNav confirmed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0009
rows.name: That's the last of 'em.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0010
rows.name: Good work. I'll let Doug know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0011
rows.name: That you, Elma?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0012
rows.name:
Sorry I'm audio-only—
we're kind of in the middle of something here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0013
rows.name: Are you in combat? We'll be right there![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0014
rows.name:
Nah, nothing you need to worry about.
We've got it under control.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0015
rows.name: Doug![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0016
rows.name: All right, listen—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0016_2
rows.name:
if you really want to help, you can pick up
my last data collection point. How's that sound?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0017
rows.name: Fair enough. But you better be careful![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0018
rows.name: Thanks, Lin. I'll throw in some chocolate for the trouble.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0019
rows.name: Hey! I want a drink too![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0020
rows.name: What?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0021
rows.name:
There's a café that makes really good cocoa.
Veeeeery expensive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0022
rows.name: Oh, heh. Yeah okay. I can make that happen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0023
rows.name: All right, see you when we're done![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0024
rows.name: Elma, you think he'll be okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0025
rows.name: I'm sure he'll be fine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0026
rows.name: Doug is a man of his word.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0027
rows.name:
Guys like him always fight harder
when they've got a promise to keep.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0028
rows.name:
Sounds like the opposite of Lao, huh?
That guy never keeps a promise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0029
rows.name:
Yeah, no kidding.
All right, let's go hold up our end of the bargain.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0030
rows.name: Time to earn that cocoa.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085609_MSG0031
rows.name: Yep![ST:wait ]
